HEADWORD: Reticulum
<hw>Re*tic"u*lum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;<plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Reticula</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L. dim. of <ets>rete</ets>
a net.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>The second stomach of
